==English==

===Pronunciation===
*/krēp/, /kriːp/, /kri:p/

===Noun===
'''creep'''  (''plural:'' '''[[creeps]]''')
# The movement of something that creeps.
# A gradual change in anything.
## (''publishing'') In sewn books, the tendancy of [[page]]s on the inside of a [[signature]] to stand out farther than those on the outside of it.
## (''materials science'') An increase in [[strain]] with time.
# (''informal'') A annoyingly [[unpleasant]] person.
#: ''Stop following me, you creep!''



