===Verb===
{{en-infl-irreg|creep|creeps|creeping|crept|crept}}
# ''(transitive):'' To move slowly with the [[abdomen]] close to the ground.
#: ''Lizards and snakes '''crept''' over the ground.''
# ''(transitive):'' Of [[plant]]s, to grow across a surface rather than upwards.
# ''(transitive):'' To move slowly and quietly in a particular direction.
#: ''He tried to '''creep''' past the guard without being seen.''
# ''(transitive):'' To change gradually in a particular direction.
#: ''Prices have been '''creeping''' up all year.''

